.Dt LL-FOOT_MDOC 1
.Os
.Sh NAME
.ll 40n
.Nm ll-foot_mdoc
.Nd line length in page headers and footers
.Sh DESCRIPTION
The right margin is reset after the end of a section,
so this text is full width again.
.Pp
.ll 40n
The line length set with
.Pf . Ic ll
only takes effect after the page header,
and it is reset to the
.Fl O Cm width No / Cm paper
default before the page footer.
